{"name":"军事后勤补给链模型","description":"后方仓库-运输线-前线三级补给链动态模型","engine":"SIMULATION_PACKAGE","simulation":{"algorithm":"RK4","time_start":0,"time_length":60,"time_step":0.5,"time_units":"DAYS"},"elements":[{"type":"STOCK","name":"后方仓库","behavior":{"initial_value":10000,"non_negative":true},"display":{"coordinates":[100,250],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"STOCK","name":"在途物资","behavior":{"initial_value":500,"non_negative":true},"display":{"coordinates":[350,250],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"STOCK","name":"前线储备","behavior":{"initial_value":1000,"non_negative":true},"display":{"coordinates":[600,250],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"生产速率","behavior":{"value":"200"},"display":{"coordinates":[100,100],"size":[110,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"运输能力","behavior":{"value":"150"},"display":{"coordinates":[300,100],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"消耗速率","behavior":{"value":"80"},"display":{"coordinates":[600,100],"size":[110,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"战斗损耗率","behavior":{"value":"0.02"},"display":{"coordinates":[720,380],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"运输延迟","behavior":{"value":"0.05"},"display":{"coordinates":[350,420],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"后方生产","from":null,"to":"后方仓库","behavior":{"value":"[生产速率]","non_negative":true},"display":{"from_coordinates":[100,180],"to_coordinates":[100,225]}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"发出物资","from":"后方仓库","to":"在途物资","behavior":{"value":"min([后方仓库], [运输能力])","non_negative":true},"display":{}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"运抵前线","from":"在途物资","to":"前线储备","behavior":{"value":"[在途物资] * [运输延迟]","non_negative":true},"display":{}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"日常消耗","from":"前线储备","to":null,"behavior":{"value":"min([前线储备], [消耗速率])","non_negative":true},"display":{"from_coordinates":[660,275],"to_coordinates":[750,250]}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"战斗损耗","from":"前线储备","to":null,"behavior":{"value":"[前线储备] * [战斗损耗率]","non_negative":true},"display":{"from_coordinates":[660,225],"to_coordinates":[750,200]}},{"type":"LINK","name":"","from":"生产速率","to":"后方生产","behavior":{}},{"type":"LINK","name":"","from":"后方仓库","to":"发出物资","behavior":{}},{"type":"LINK","name":"","from":"运输能力","to":"发出物资","behavior":{}},{"type":"LINK","name":"","from":"在途物资","to":"运抵前线","behavior":{}},{"type":"LINK","name":"","from":"运输延迟","to":"运抵前线","behavior":{}},{"type":"LINK","name":"","from":"前线储备","to":"日常消耗","behavior":{}},{"type":"LINK","name":"","from":"消耗速率","to":"日常消耗","behavior":{}},{"type":"LINK","name":"","from":"前线储备","to":"战斗损耗","behavior":{}},{"type":"LINK","name":"","from":"战斗损耗率","to":"战斗损耗","behavior":{}}],"visualizations":[{"type":"TIME_SERIES","name":"补给链动态","elements":["后方仓库","在途物资","前线储备"]}]}